							<h4 class="caption font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Key features</h4>
							<ul class="space-y-2">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2 body-text"><span class="text-accent-yellow">-</span>Unified message format (role + content blocks)</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2 body-text"><span class="text-accent-yellow">-</span>Built-in conversation history management</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2 body-text"><span class="text-accent-yellow">-</span>Native tool_use / tool_result blocks</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2 body-text"><span class="text-accent-yellow">-</span>System prompt as first-class parameter</li>
