						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">StartIngestionJob</span> — sync docs into vector store</li>
						<li class="body-text text-ink-muted">Also: Get, Update, Delete, List variants</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="card p-5">
					<h4 class="heading-3 mb-3">Agents</h4>
