						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">CreateAgent</span> — define instructions + model</li>
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">CreateAgentActionGroup</span> — add Lambda/API tools</li>
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">PrepareAgent</span> — compile for deployment</li>
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">CreateAgentAlias</span> — version for production</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="card p-5">
					<h4 class="heading-3 mb-3">Prompts & Flows</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">CreatePrompt</span> — centralized template</li>
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">CreatePromptVersion</span> — immutable snapshot</li>
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">CreateFlow / PrepareFlow</span> — visual workflows</li>
						<li class="body-text"><span class="text-accent-aqua font-semibold">ValidateFlowDefinition</span> — check for errors</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="card p-5">
					<h4 class="heading-3 mb-3">Guardrails & Evaluation</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-2">
